snippet.title: Motherboard
snippet.description:
Motherboard is VICE’s tech desk. We believe that tech should work for people, and in holding its gatekeepers accountable. Through investigative reporting, sharp commentary, digital video, and more, Motherboard is a unique and conversation-starting source for expert and immersive coverage of the technology changing our present and future.
